These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk
There 2 different types of food: apple, pomegranate
1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda |
| Food       | apple | pomegranate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | coffee |
| Sport      | cycling     | volleyball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, satire
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian
1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | satire  |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
